data.description: Spectacular 5 Bedroom home with an incredible yard, amazing rooftop deck, coffee bar nook, professional home gym (garage currently used as gym) and so much more! Newer roof, windows, walls, flooring, electric, plumbing, energy-efficient furnace, hot water heater, central air, Osmosis water filtration system in kitchen - the list goes on! Foyer leads to formal living room with bay window. Dining room great for holiday dinners, friends/family gatherings. French doors lead to main floor 5th bedroom, ideal 2nd family room/man cave/play room. 4 bedrooms upstairs, Master Bedroom w/private bath and a spacious rooftop deck perfect for your morning coffee or end of day relaxing- check out that view! Kitchen has breakfast bar, eating area, newer energy-efficient appliances and opens to large family room w/wood-burning fireplace. Sliders to patio for relaxing on summer evenings. The yard is over 1/3 acre, and so peaceful! Moen fixtures, custom window treatments. Pull down attic stairs in garage; cement crawl approx. 4 ft. This is a great home! Come see it today!  Seller is leaving riding lawnmower (valued over $2000) for new owner!
